+ 
+	  The API is not backwards compatible with BlueZ 4. 
+ 
+	  Bluez utils will use systemd and/or udev if enabled. 
+ 
+	  http://www.bluez.org
+	  http://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/bluetooth
+ 
+if BR2_PACKAGE_BLUEZ5_UTILS 
